  b) No Tampering with Copyright and Display Content: It is strictly
  prohibited to develop projects that remove, minimize, obscure, or
  modify Team APE:RIP copyright notices, team identifiers, or any
  notifications in the Software. It is strictly prohibited to use code
  modifications or third-party injections to obscure, remove, or
  modify any advertisements or sponsorship content displayed in the
  main interface or elsewhere; the foregoing restrictions also apply
  to the relevant displayed content in built-in tools and built-in
